{"tid":7573,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有錢人船P, 窮撚勿入。","createTime":"2016-11-28T01:34:31.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T14:16:37.000Z","uid":8098,"like":4,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd4094e9548c6ac17c10ddc6e9057ba7918978a3","tid":7573,"uid":8098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T01:34:31.000Z","msg":"是咁的，呢個星期五，我唔去浦了。夜晚出海。<br />\n我地book 了3 隻船。第一隻  Adela , 租的。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.adela.com.hk/index.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.adela.com.hk%2Findex.php&d=YDpFvmEDpF5LG4WvhAwVkcW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=ef0c4d16\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.adela.com.hk/index.php</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://i51.tinypic.com/m4qog.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi51.tinypic.com%2Fm4qog.jpg&h=35e3bc06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i56.tinypic.com/idwxuv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi56.tinypic.com%2Fidwxuv.jpg&h=315ca61e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i53.tinypic.com/2ldit53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi53.tinypic.com%2F2ldit53.jpg&h=ebde5b6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n坐50人的，長80幾呎。<br />\n<br />\n另一隻, 私伙的 Princess V62  坐20人 西班牙式遊艇<br />\n<img src=\"http://i54.tinypic.com/snf8zo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi54.tinypic.com%2Fsnf8zo.png&h=b8394965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i53.tinypic.com/sblb9u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi53.tinypic.com%2Fsblb9u.png&h=291b1e46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i55.tinypic.com/2iw93x5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi55.tinypic.com%2F2iw93x5.png&h=183cfd08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i56.tinypic.com/zwl47p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi56.tinypic.com%2Fzwl47p.png&h=01d0ddbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i55.tinypic.com/52nct5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi55.tinypic.com%2F52nct5.png&h=05bfa3b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i51.tinypic.com/21cgwns.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi51.tinypic.com%2F21cgwns.png&h=cfcd9a8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我中意呢隻多d，入少少，寫意d。<br />\n<br />\n重有一隻普通 中式船。<br />\n<br />\n搞手會買好多酒。<br />\n<br />\n星期五 , 7點尖沙咀碼頭集合<br />\n<br />\n男仔：$1000 位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女仔：Model , 靚女免費。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n普通女仔：唔俾去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n來吧靚女，識d俾得起$1000去船河的人吧。<br />\n<br />\np.s. 呢d船河無得賺，搞手只求打個和，大家開開心心玩返晚。"},{"pid":"52307cb34426d2a27d72b26941f807046ec16a51","tid":7573,"uid":3518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T01:35:18.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7caeeb0d2af16a08e5b64766e74b3ff5f3ac858","tid":7573,"uid":8098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T01:36:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收皮啦死窮撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70225f0a326c05fec4fe4a9b36634114f2ff97f7","tid":7573,"uid":3108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T01:38:36.000Z","msg":"死圖喎"},{"pid":"073af76e7719b857519e9f8343f3d1f7592d5c87","tid":7573,"uid":8098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T01:39:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死圖喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有錢人會知係咩款的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"454610bccc07d908c0478bb3f1d8afe3554f96c4","tid":7573,"uid":31925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T01:48:59.000Z","msg":"負皮，上一頁"},{"pid":"3ef8b40d3980fa843fabab751116b1f167332d20","tid":757